  <name>Stamina</name>
  <summary>Focus timer with programming language tracking</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Stamina is a productivity application that helps you maintain focus
      using the Pomodoro Technique. It alternates between focus sessions
      and breaks to optimize productivity.
    </p>
    <p>Key features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Customizable focus and break durations</li>
      <li>Track time spent on different programming languages</li>
      <li>Statistics and progress tracking</li>
      <li>Dark/light theme support</li>
      <li>Keyboard shortcuts for quick control</li>
      <li>Notifications and sound alerts</li>
      <li>Automatic session switching</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
